{
  "texts": [
    "The science fiction narrative of literary creation presents the cyber-virtual space in a highly figurative form, which is highly consistent with the technical characteristics and conceptual connotation of the current \"metaverse\" [25].",
    "The digital cultural capital market has helped to popularise the concept of \" metaverse \".",
    "In October 2021, Facebook founder Mark Zuckerberg announced that the company would change its name to \"Meta\", and in November the same year, Microsoft also announced that it would integrate virtual environment technology to create a \"meta verse\".",
    "Rob-lox identifies the eight elements of the metaverse as identity, sociability, immersion, low latency, diversity, location, economic system and civilisation.",
    "As a virtual world based on reality, video games provide a natural convenience for the formation of the technical space and conceptual connotation of the \"metaverse\"."
  ]
}